summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of elevated structures and approaches thereto, on Southwest Spokane Street and other streets; providing for the widening of South and Southwest Spokane Street, Deiridge Way Southwest and East Marginal Way South; providing for approaches to said elevated structures; providing for the acquisition of right-of-way necessary therefor; providing for changing and establishing of the necessary grades; providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor.
